commit message:
Add an alias for texting applications.

I did not bother installing a dev environment for that, hence, it is not tested. I used [1] as my resource, not sure if this is adequate.

[1]: http://developer.android.com/reference/android/content/Intent.html#CATEGORY_APP_MESSAGING
Merge branch 'patch-1' of https://github.com/padenot/Summon into padenot-patch-1
Display 'search button' instead of enter key

Use holder instead of record.

Faster data transfer
Better architecture

Warning: breaks alias and history, will be amended in future commit
No more record in controller parts
Automatic lowerCase for query and providers
